### Health Check API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### ==============================================
### HEALTH CHECK ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================

### Get Health Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: {{contentType}}

# Response 200 OK:
# {
#   "status": "success",
#   "data": {
#     "database": "UP",
#     "app": "UP",
#     "timestamp": "2026-02-11T10:30:00Z",
#     "databaseCountCheck": 5
#   },
#   "message": "All systems operational"
# }

###

### ==============================================
### CONTACT MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================

### Get Contact Endpoint Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Accept: {{contentType}}

# Response 200 OK:
# {
#   "status": "success",
#   "data": "Use POST with JSON body to submit the contact form."
# }

###

### Submit Contact Form - Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Talha Ahmed",
  "email": "talha@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "9876543210",
  "college": "IIT Delhi",
  "yearOfStudy": "2nd Year",
  "branch": "CSE",
  "hearAboutUs": "WhatsApp Group",
  "hearAboutUsOther": null
}

# Response 200 OK:
# {
#   "status": "success",
#   "data": "Message sent successfully! We'll get back to you soon."
# }

###

### Submit Contact Form - Invalid Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "email": "not-a-valid-email",
  "phoneNumber": "1234567890",
  "college": "Test College",
  "yearOfStudy": "1st Year",
  "branch": "IT",
  "hearAboutUs": "Google"
}

# Response 400 Bad Request:
# {
#   "status": "error",
#   "data": "Invalid request body. Please send JSON with application/json Content-Type."
# }

###

### Get Failed Contact Submissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/failed
Accept: {{contentType}}

# Response 200 OK:
# {
#   "status": "success",
#   "data": [
#     {
#       "id": 1,
#       "fullName": "Test User",
#       "email": "test@example.com",
#       "status": "EMAIL_FAILED",
#       "submittedAt": "2026-02-11T10:00:00",
#       "expiresAt": "2026-03-13T10:00:00"
#     }
#   ]
# }

###

### ==============================================
### EM (EMIRATIYO INVESTMENTS) CONTACT ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================

### Get EM Contact Endpoint Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/em/contact
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Submit EM Contact Form - Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/em/contact
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Talha Ahmed",
  "company": "Emiratiyo Investments",
  "phone": "+971501234567",
  "email": "talha@example.com",
  "subject": "Investment Inquiry",
  "message": "Hello, I want to know more about your services."
}

###

### Submit EM Contact Form - Invalid Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/em/contact
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "company": "Test Company",
  "phone": "+971501234567",
  "email": "not-a-valid-email",
  "subject": "Test",
  "message": "Hi"
}

###

### Get Failed EM Contact Submissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/em/contact/failed
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### ==============================================
### TCS "NOTIFY ME" (COMING SOON) ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================

### Get Notify Me Endpoint Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notify-me
Accept: {{contentType}}

###

### Submit Notify Me Signup - Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notify-me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Talha Ahmed",
  "email": "talha@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "9876543210"
}

###

### Submit Notify Me Signup - Duplicate (same email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/notify-me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Talha Ahmed Updated",
  "email": "talha@example.com",
  "phoneNumber": "9876543210"
}

###

### Get Failed Notify Me Signups
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notify-me/failed
Accept: {{contentType}}

###